OL,3,CSurgeon who had legs amputated accused
OL,4,Cof falsely claiming he had sepsis
OL,6,FHopper is due before Magistrates in
OL,7,FBodmin on Wednesday accused of two
OL,8,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,9,Frepresentation, and a charge of
OL,10,Fencouraging or assisting in the
OL,11,Fcommission of an indictable-only
OL,12,Foffence, namely grievous bodily harm.
OL,14,FIt is alleged that on dates between
OL,15,FJune 3 and June 26 2019, Hopper
OL,16,Fdishonestly made a false
OL,17,Frepresentation to insurers claiming
OL,18,Fthat his leg injuries were the "result
OL,19,Fof sepsis and were not self-inflicted".
