OL,6,FIt is also alleged that between 21
OL,7,FAugust 2018 and 4 December 2020,
OL,8,FHopper bought videos from The
OL,9,FEunuchMaker website showing the
OL,10,Fremoval of limbs, which "encouraged
OL,11,FMarius Gustavson to remove body parts
OL,12,Fof third parties".
OL,14,FHopper has not worked at the Royal
OL,15,FCornwall Hospitals NHS Trust since
OL,16,FMarch 2023.
