OL,6,FThe Medical Practitioners Tribunal
OL,7,FService's interim orders tribunal
OL,8,Fplaced restrictions on his practice
OL,9,Fthe following month while the General
OL,10,FMedical Council investigated, and he
OL,11,Fhas been suspended from the medical
OL,12,Fregister since December 2023.
OL,14,FA Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,15,Fspokeswoman said: "The Royal Cornwall
OL,16,FHospitals NHS Trust, where Mr Hopper
OL,17,Fhas been employed, has worked closely
OL,18,Fwith Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,19,Fthroughout the investigation."
